    measurement: "Dated falsifiers calendared and self-graded — the thesis as the ledger's biggest Gnomon entry, 099's discipline at full scale.",
    synthesis: "The capstone synthesis: reads the whole bank's residue as evidence, prices its own wager (judgment capital), and closes the loop with pattern #1 at industry scale.",
    altitude: "One thesis, two rooms — the board gets allocation with markers, the panel gets structure plus tension; neither gets a hedge.",
    transfer: "The global bottleneck read IS the transfer: every seat this bank targets — CAPE, MAI, FDE, TPM — is a bet on where the constraint moves, and the discipline of calling it with falsifiers is the job description underneath all of them.",
